io.swagger.v3.oas.annotations.info

Annotation Type Info


  • @Target(value=ANNOTATION_TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Inherited
public @interface Info
    The annotation may be used in OpenAPIDefinition.info() to populate the Info section of the OpenAPI document.
    See Also:
    Info (OpenAPI specification), OpenAPIDefinition

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements

      A URL to the Terms of Service for the API.
